ygData.messageBody:
The lesser dragon is only around 27th lvl. He can be found on the buttom
lvl of upper Guk. Went looking for him a little while ago, but was only
20th and the mobs were still a bit rough, will be heading back there once I
hit 24th and will let you all know what I find ;)

Talarin, High Elven Wizard
